prompt:
Patient: Hello?

Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Simone McKloskey?

Patient: Hello? Yes. It is.

Nurse: Thank you for confirming. Could you please provide your date of birth for verification purposes?

Patient: August third nineteen eighty two.

Nurse: Thank you for confirming, Ms. McKloskey. I'm calling about your upcoming total knee replacement. Is this a good time to talk?

Patient: Yes.

responses.gpt4: Great! Thank you for taking the time. I hope you're having a good day. Could you share a bit about how your day has been so far?
responses.our_model: Excellent, thank you for your time, Ms. McKloskey. I hope your day is going well so far. Can you share a bit about how you've been feeling today?
